item.description:
Hi ladies!

It's been a little while since the last meet-up (my apologies).

Let's get together before the holidays one last time and dance, eat, play pool, and socialize at the Charlie Horse in West Bridgewater. This place has something for every taste in entertainment....not to mention really good food!

The band usually goes on between 9.45-10pm so I figured we could trickle in around 9 and get ourselves situated.

Cover is between $7 to get in (unless they have changed it??) and the food and drinks are very reasonably priced.

Please note that I have increased my annual membership dues to $5.00. This is a one time annual fee and it helps me keep the group running, as I have to pay quarterly dues to keep a Meet Up group active. You can either pay via Paypal or in cash when you see me.

Thanks and I looking forward to seeing everyone!

Lisa

PS. As the date nears- I will send an email out with my cell # and where we plan to meet to make it easier for everyone to connect once inside the bar.
item.name: Dick and Jane play at The Charlie Horse
